<h1>Record Change Notification</h1>

<p>Hello <%= @user.name.presence || @user.email %>,</p>

<p>A record has been <strong><%= @change_type %></strong>.</p>

<ul>
	<li><strong>What changed:</strong> <%= @change_message.presence || "No details available." %></li>
	<li><strong>Item:</strong> <%= @item_name.presence || "Not specified" %></li>
	<li><strong>Changed by:</strong> <%= @actor&.name.presence || @actor&.email || "Unknown user" %></li>
	<li><strong>Changed at:</strong> <%= (@changed_at || Time.current).in_time_zone.strftime("%Y-%m-%d %H:%M %Z") %></li>
</ul>

<p>This is an automated notification to inform you of the recent change.</p>